trans-unit.source: Provides a wrapper for converting server components into client script.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en tekstbryting for å konvertere serverkomponenter til klientskript.

trans-unit.source: This class uses an internal dictionary to hold references to components, elements, properties, and events.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen bruker en intern ordlisten til å inneholde referanser til komponenter, elementer, egenskaper og hendelser.

trans-unit.source: To populate this dictionary, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddComponentProperty%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddElementProperty%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddProperty%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddEvent%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: For å fylle ut denne ordlisten, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddComponentProperty%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddElementProperty%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddProperty%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddEvent%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddEvent%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddProperty%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddElementProperty%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.AddComponentProperty%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you are finished, call the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.GetScript%2A> method to generate the client script.
trans-unit.target: Når du er ferdig, kaller den <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.GetScript%2A>metode for å generere klienten skript</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptComponentDescriptor.GetScript%2A>
